        <developed_by>InVigor™ Canola</developed_by>
        <has_no_requirement>labelling</has_no_requirement>
        <tolerance_to_herbicide>glufosinate</tolerance_to_herbicide>
        <rdfs:comment>Canola variety that has ability to eliminate glufosinate herbicidal activity, metabolise antibiotic, and create fertility restoration. The herbicide tolerance trait resulted from the expression of bar gene derived from Streptomyces hygroscopicus; the antibiotic resistance trait resulted from nptll gene derived from Escherichia coli Tn5 transposon; the fertility restoration resulted from barstar gene derived from Bacillus amyloliquefaciens.</rdfs:comment>
