        <resistance_to_insect>Lepidopteran</resistance_to_insect>
        <rdfs:comment>Roce variety that has can do selection for resistance to the antibiotic hygromycin B and confers resistance to lepidopteran insects by selectively damaging their midgut lining from selection by using aph4 (hpt) marker of Escherichia coli and gene overexpresion of cry1Ab from Bacillus thuringiensis subsp. kumamotoensis</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:comment>https://www.isaaa.org/gmapprovaldatabase/event/default.asp?EventID=221&amp;Event=Tarom%20molaii%20+%20cry1Ab
https://www.fao.org/food/food-safety-quality/gm-foods-platform/browse-information-by/oecd-unique-identifier/oecd-unique-identifier-details/en/?ui=287745</rdfs:comment>
    </owl:NamedIndividual>
    


