        <rdfs:comment>Sugarcane variety that has ability to decrease glyphosate herbicide binding affinity and to metabolise neomycin and kanamycin antibiotics. The herbicide tolerance trait expressed from the introduction of cp4 epsps transgene derived from Agrobacterium tumefaciens strain CP4 and the antibiotic resistance trait expressed from the introduction of nptll selection marker gene derived from Escherichia coli Tn5 transposon</rdfs:comment>
