        <hasTrait rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/90958855/ontologies/2024/8/riesma_thesis#herbicide_tolerance"/>
        <rdfs:comment>a design to exhibits tolerance to oxyfluorfen herbicide through chemical mutagenesis and conventional breeding methods resulting in a single nucleotide deletion of guanine in Exon 8 at position 1699 in the UGP3 gene that results in truncation at amino acid 584 in the ROXY® rice Uridine diphosphate (UDP)-Glucose Pyrophosphorylase 3 (UGP3) enzyme.</rdfs:comment>
    </owl:NamedIndividual>
    


