        <has_new_protein>dicamba mono-oxygenase</has_new_protein>
        <rdfs:comment>a design to create dicamba herbicide tolerance by using trangenics technology
the gene dmo derived from Stenotrophomonas maltophilia strain DI-6 overexpression produces dicamba mono-oxygenase enzyme that can confers tolerance to the herbicide dicamba by using dicamba as substrate in an enzymatic reaction</rdfs:comment>
    </owl:NamedIndividual>
    


