        <rdfs:comment>Although the M-521 variety has been released, the new-use label for the companion ROXY® herbicide that will be partnered with the ROXY® variety to make up the ROXY® Rice Production System (ROXY® RPS) is awaiting EPA approval. Therefore, seed production and the commercial launch of the ROXY® RPS will be on hold until the herbicide label is approved.
