        <rdfs:comment>a design to create mannose metabolism ability in the plant resulted from the expresion of pmi gene derived from Eschericia coli to produce Phosphomannose Isomerase (PMI) enzyme that allows positive selection for recovery of transformed plants.</rdfs:comment>
