        <hasTrait rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/90958855/ontologies/2024/8/riesma_thesis#insect_resistance"/>
        <has_new_protein>chimeric (cry) delta endotoxin</has_new_protein>
        <rdfs:comment>a design to create insect resistance trait by using transgenic techonogy.
the gene introduced in cry gene derived from Bacillus thuringiensis, the transgene over expression creates toxins that will damage the insect&apos;s midgut lining</rdfs:comment>
    </owl:NamedIndividual>
    


